@startuml
title Enrich Stage - Class Diagram (Current)
set namespaceSeparator none
left to right direction
hide empty members
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #f7e9dc
  BorderColor #d9c2a8
}

class PipelineContainer {
  + enrich_stage(): EnrichStage
  + pipeline_composer(): PipelineComposer
}

class StageFactory {
  + create(stage_type, spec, ctx, **kwargs)
}

class PipelineOrchestrator {
  + run(source): Iterable[TransformResult]
}

class EnrichUseCase {
  + run(row_source, pipeline, dataset, logger, run_id, report, catalog): CommandResult
}

class EnrichStage {
  - enricher: EnricherEngine
  - catalog: ErrorCatalog
  + run(source): Iterable[TransformResult]
}

class EnricherEngine {
  - core: EnricherCore
  + __init__(spec, ctx, ..., providers, options, sink_spec, run_id)
  + enrich(result): TransformResult
}

class EnricherDsl {
  - registry: OperationRegistry
  - providers: ProviderGateway
  + compile(spec: EnrichSpec): EnricherSpec
}

class EnricherCore {
  - spec: EnricherSpec
  - deps: object
  - secret_store: SecretStoreProtocol?
  - dataset: str
  - catalog: ErrorCatalog
  - sink_spec: SinkSpec?
  - run_id: str?
  - conflict_resolver: ConflictResolver
  - merge_engine: MergeEngine
  + enrich(result): TransformResult
  - _execute_operation(...): OperationReport
  - _collect_candidates(...)
  - _apply_candidates(...): OperationReport
  - _store_secrets(...): None
}

class ConflictResolver {
  + decide(candidates): CandidateDecision
}

class MergeEngine {
  - authoritative_sources: set[str]
  + should_apply(current, candidate, policy): bool
}

class _FieldMutationTracker {
  + has_writer(field): bool
  + register(field, op_name): None
}

class EnricherReport {
  + operations_total: int
  + outcomes: dict[str, int]
  + updated_fields: int
  + record(report): None
  + as_dict(): dict[str, Any]
}

class ProviderGateway {
  + with_defaults(): ProviderGateway
  + lookup(name, deps, value, args): list[dict[str, Any]]
  + exists(name, deps, value, args): Any|None
}

class OperationRegistry

class EnricherSpec {
  + operations: tuple[EnrichmentOperation, ...]
  + key_registry: KeyRegistry
  + source_priorities: dict[str, int]
  + default_merge_policy: MergePolicy
  + default_strictness: StrictnessPolicy
  + authoritative_sources: set[str]
  + is_fatal_error: callable?
  + stop_on_failed: bool
}

class EnrichmentOperation {
  + name: str
  + op_type: EnrichOperationType
  + targets: tuple[str, ...]
  + required_keys: tuple[str, ...]
  + providers: tuple[CandidateProvider, ...]
  + merge_policy: MergePolicy?
  + strictness: StrictnessPolicy?
  + run_when_errors: RunWhenErrors
}

class EnrichContext {
  + dataset: str
  + run_id: str?
  + as_of: Any?
}

class CandidateProvider <<protocol>> {
  + fetch(ctx, result, deps, key_values): list[CandidateValue]
}

class CandidateValue {
  + field: str
  + value: Any
  + source: str
  + priority: int?
  + confidence: float?
}

class CandidateDecision {
  + status: str
  + selected: CandidateValue?
  + candidates: list[CandidateValue]
}

class OperationReport {
  + op: str
  + outcome: EnrichOutcome
  + events: list[EnrichEvent]
  + resolve_hints: list[ResolveHint]
  + warnings: list[DiagnosticItem]
  + errors: list[DiagnosticItem]
}

class ResolveHint {
  + field: str
  + lookup_key: dict[str, Any]
  + reason: str
  + candidates: list[dict[str, Any]]
}

class EnrichEvent {
  + op: str
  + field: str
  + before: Any
  + after: Any
  + source: str
  + decision: str
  + outcome: str
}

class EnrichOutcome <<enum>> {
  APPLIED
  SKIPPED
  WARNED
  FAILED
  NEEDS_RESOLVE
}

class RunWhenErrors <<enum>> {
  NEVER
  ONLY_NON_FATAL
  ALWAYS
}

class EnrichOperationType <<enum>> {
  COMPUTE
  FILL_MISSING
  LOOKUP
  GENERATE
  MEMBERSHIP
}

class MergePolicy
class StrictnessPolicy
class EnrichSpec
class SinkSpec
class StageExecutionContext
class ErrorCatalog
class EnrichLookupPort <<protocol>>
class DictionaryProviderPort <<protocol>>
class SecretStoreProtocol <<protocol>>
class "TransformResult<T>" as TransformResultT

' Entry / boundary touchpoints
PipelineContainer --> StageFactory : enrich stage created via create(...)
PipelineContainer --> EnrichUseCase : enrich command path
PipelineContainer --> ProviderGateway : shared default providers
EnrichUseCase --> PipelineOrchestrator : ENRICH checkpoint pipeline
PipelineOrchestrator --> EnrichStage : run(stream)

' Stage / engine / core
EnrichStage --> EnricherEngine
EnrichStage --> ErrorCatalog : diagnostic_boundary(ENRICH)
EnricherEngine --> EnricherDsl : compile EnrichSpec -> EnricherSpec
EnricherEngine --> EnricherCore : delegates runtime enrich
EnricherEngine --> StageExecutionContext : ctx.get(...) / metadata
EnricherEngine --> EnrichSpec
EnricherEngine --> SinkSpec

' DSL compile path and compiled models
EnricherDsl --> OperationRegistry
EnricherDsl --> ProviderGateway
EnricherDsl --> EnrichSpec
EnricherDsl --> EnricherSpec
EnricherSpec o-- EnrichmentOperation
EnrichmentOperation --> CandidateProvider
EnrichmentOperation --> MergePolicy
EnrichmentOperation --> StrictnessPolicy
EnrichmentOperation --> EnrichOperationType
EnrichmentOperation --> RunWhenErrors

' Core enrich mechanics
EnricherCore --> EnricherSpec
EnricherCore --> ConflictResolver
EnricherCore --> MergeEngine
EnricherCore ..> _FieldMutationTracker : per-record mutation tracking
EnricherCore ..> EnricherReport : per-record summary
EnricherCore ..> EnrichContext : per-record runtime context
EnricherCore ..> OperationReport
EnricherCore ..> CandidateValue
EnricherCore ..> CandidateDecision
EnricherCore ..> ResolveHint : meta.resolve_requests[]
EnricherCore ..> EnrichEvent : meta.enrich_events[]
EnricherCore ..> EnrichOutcome
EnricherCore --> ErrorCatalog
EnricherCore --> SinkSpec : validate_sink_fields(...)
EnricherCore --> SecretStoreProtocol : put_many(...)
EnricherCore ..> EnrichLookupPort : provider-backed lookup via deps.cache_gateway
EnricherCore ..> DictionaryProviderPort : provider-backed lookup via deps.dictionaries
EnricherCore ..> TransformResultT

' Runtime provider and ports
ProviderGateway ..> EnrichLookupPort : cache.by_field / cache.exists_by_field
ProviderGateway ..> DictionaryProviderPort : dictionary.* providers
CandidateProvider ..> ProviderGateway : compiled providers use gateway

' Layout helpers
PipelineContainer -[hidden]-> EnrichUseCase
EnrichUseCase -[hidden]-> EnrichStage
EnrichStage -[hidden]-> EnricherEngine
EnricherEngine -[hidden]-> EnricherCore
EnricherCore -[hidden]-> ConflictResolver
ConflictResolver -[hidden]-> MergeEngine
EnricherDsl -[hidden]-> ProviderGateway
ProviderGateway -[hidden]-> EnrichLookupPort
EnrichLookupPort -[hidden]-> SecretStoreProtocol

note right of EnricherEngine
EnricherEngine is a thin DSL/runtime wrapper:
- compiles EnrichSpec into EnricherSpec (EnricherDsl)
- builds EnricherCore
- pulls ports/metadata from StageExecutionContext (ctx path)
- builds a lightweight deps namespace for provider-backed operations
end note

note right of EnricherCore
Core owns enrich mechanics only:
- per-op execution with strictness/run_when_errors
- candidate collection (compute/generate/provider.fetch)
- conflict resolution + merge policy + sink validation
- resolve hints/events/summary in meta
- secret storage + masking/clearing secret fields
end note

note bottom of EnricherCore
Downstream touchpoint:
ambiguous enrich results are materialized as `meta.resolve_requests`
for later match/resolve pipeline stages.
end note

@enduml
